					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If I remember well the CL/SL pads selects between MMC5 and PPU for the lower 3 or 4 address lines.<br />This means if you solder them to the PPU the MMC5 has no control on the fine scroll, but only on coarse scroll. I guess it'll count as a &quot;weird rounding behaviour&quot; as you put it.<br /><br />I tried switching Just Breed to CL and SL mode but there was no difference at all.</div>

